des: 107.1 The Zone is Southeast Missouri’s premiere rock radio station. We provide our listeners with the greatest rock music from the 1970’s to current. The Zone has great LOCAL shows such as The Lunch Zone, The Number 2 Show, The 80’s Hard Drive @ 5, Dinner With…, And The Friday Night Cruise all hosted by LOCAL DJ’s who live in the area! Artists you will hear on The Zone range from Aerosmith, AC/DC, Nazareth, Linkin Park, Disturbed, and many, many more!
